    {
      "text": "Bio-ship Paladin, known in Japan as Space Battleship Gomora, is a 1990 horizontally scrolling shooter video game developed and published by UPL for arcades. It was released in Japan in November 1990 and in North America by Sammy Corporation in North America in April 1991. It was later ported to the Sega Mega Drive. Hamster Corporation released the game as part of their Arcade Archives series for the Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 in August 2021.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
